name: SWYP Foundation
description: SWYP Token is a revolutionary digital asset positioned at the convergence of traditional and decentralized finance. Built on the Binance Smart Chain, it offers seamless tokenization of real-world assets such as real estate, Forex, and bullion. With its Web 3.0 framework, SWYP aims to modernize financial interactions by blending traditional assets with decentralized systems, enhancing liquidity, transparency, and accessibility in the global financial landscape.
